posts.subject: Formatting?
posts.body: Wrong board probably, but what are all options for formatting in 08ch? I know there are **spoilers**, ==Red Text==, __underline__ and ~~crossline~~, ''cursive'' and '''bold''', just like in original 8ch. How do you make a code block though? And is there anything else I have missed?
For some reason whenever I click on a thumbnail instead of showing the full image on the same page it opens the image's link.
